* [[火星15彈道飛彈|火星15彈道飛彈]]：射程12,000－13,000公里
* [[火星17彈道飛彈|火星17彈道飛彈]]：射程至少13,000公里<ref>[https://www.iiss.org/blogs/analysis/2020/10/north-korea-missile-parade What North Korea’s latest missile parade tells us, and what it doesn’t]. ''[[International_Institute_for_Strategic_Studies|International Institute for Strategic Studies]]''. 12 October 2020.</ref>

